examples.en: A writer's style must develop organically.
The land has been farmed organically since 1995.
This neighborhood is an organic part of the city.
Fruit and vegetables should ideally be organically grown.
Farmers lack any incentive to manage their land organically.
The symbol on the packet is a guarantee that the food has been produced organically.
He thinks of the city not as a collection of different neighborhoods but as an organic whole.
Perhaps he was organically of that cheerful and easy nature, which is content to enjoy the present, and not brood over the past.
